            <l><anchor id="struct16a" /><pb type="text" rend="supp" n="143" ed="V" />Lad i Jesu Kristi Navn,<anchor id="struct16b" /></l>
            <l><anchor id="struct17a" />Dig til &#x00C6;re, os til Gavn,<anchor id="struct17b" /></l>
